453.
991Hetuṃ maggārammaṇaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca hetu maggārammaṇo dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā…  tīṇi.
992Nahetuṃ maggārammaṇaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca nahetu maggārammaṇo dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā…  tīṇi.
993Hetuṃ maggārammaṇañca nahetuṃ maggārammaṇañca dhammaṃ paṭicca hetu maggārammaṇo dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā…  tīṇi. (Saṃkhittaṃ.)
454.
994Hetuyā nava, ārammaṇe nava, adhipatiyā nava…pe…  kamme nava…pe…  avigate nava. (Saṃkhittaṃ.)
